to the state pen.

155
00:11:11,629 --> 00:11:15,131
Tommy, l know you
and the wife will be hurtin',

156
00:11:15,299 --> 00:11:18,301
workin' hard to cover
Eddie's ass like this,

157
00:11:18,469 --> 00:11:21,304
