283
00:23:25,779 --> 00:23:28,030
l don't want that.

284
00:23:33,703 --> 00:23:36,872
Tommy.

285
00:23:37,040 --> 00:23:38,916
l just--

286
00:23:39,084 --> 00:23:41,710
take care of yourself, bro.

